8.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2024_industry_bbc_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2024_industry_bbc_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2024_industry_bbc_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3799017" class="wp-caption-text"> Robert (Harry Lawtey) and Henry (Kit Harington) in season three of &#39;Industry&#39; CREDIT: HBO / Nick Strasburg</figcaption></figure><p> Lawtey&#39;s exit from the show also serves as a rather natural farewell for his character. At the end of <em>Industry</em> &#39;s third season, Lawtey&#39;s Spearing quitting Pierpoint to work at a psilocybin startup. While this was meant to build to a larger storyline for Spearing in season four, it seems as though his story will continue offscreen.</p><p> <em>Industry</em> has been an acclaimed series throughout its run and has catapulted several of its cast into superstardom, including <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/here-are-all-the-winners-from-the-baftas-2025-3838432">David Jonnson, who has won the EE Rising Star Award at the BAFTAs earlier this week</a> . <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/bafta-rising-star-nominees-dominated-by-industry-alumni-3826919">Also nominated were his <em>Industry</em> cast mates Marisa Abela and Nabhaan Rizwan</a> . </p><figure id="attachment_3800280" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3800280" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3800280" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Industry-season-3.jpg" alt="Industry season three" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Industry-season-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Industry-season-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Industry-season-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Industry-season-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Industry-season-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Industry-season-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3800280" class="wp-caption-text"> Industry season three. CREDIT: BBC/Bad Wolf Productions/HBO/Marc Hom</figcaption></figure><p> Harry Lawtey has also risen to fame, most recently appearing in <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/joker-folie-a-deux"><em>Joker: Folie à Deux</em></a> as Harvey Dent.</p><p> Season three of <em>Industry</em> saw the addition of Kit Harington, and the show was <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/industry-fans-call-season-three-finale-one-of-the-best-ever-tv-episodes-3798170">praised by fans as some of the “best ever” episodes of television</a> . The finale was also hailed as “one of the greatest season finales I&#39;ve ever watched”, “momentous” and “insanely good” by fans.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/harry-lawtey-exits-industry-season-four-3840040">Harry Lawtey exits &#39;Industry&#39; season four</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
